Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴  我進來咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  大小姐  請稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.60,0:00:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒準備好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.13,0:00:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.84,0:00:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二學期要開始居然會讓你這麼憂鬱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…沒有那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你怦怦直跳的  最近有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要獨自全部承擔哦  昴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.35,0:00:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.35,0:00:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是和次郎同學有關的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如被問及「今天內衣的花紋是什麼樣的」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.00,0:00:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的  但有什麼煩惱的話要跟我說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我踢！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.06,0:01:15.10,frame,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#########OP對幀#########
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.14,0:01:21.89,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今  胸に生まれた  揺るぎないこの気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.14,0:01:21.89,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在誕生在胸中的  這不可動搖的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:27.61,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}抱きしめて翔べ  遥か遠く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:27.61,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}緊緊擁抱著  飛向遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:45.42,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ゲームセットなんてない日々  イメージして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:45.42,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}漫無止盡的日子  盡情想像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:50.84,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}叶えたい未来  数えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:50.84,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}把想要實現的未來  細細數清
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:56.72,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}打ち明け合ったら約束  あきらめない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:56.72,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}互相約定  決不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.89,0:02:01.81,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢を形にするまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.89,0:02:01.81,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}直到夢想成形之時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.02,0:02:07.40,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好きなこと  全力で追いかけようよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.02,0:02:07.40,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}喜愛的事情  就要努力地去追尋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.61,0:02:15.07,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一緒に…ね！？  楽しくね！！  希望の羽を広げて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.61,0:02:15.07,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一起來  開心地  展開希望的雙翅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:21.83,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今  胸に生まれた  揺るぎないこの気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:21.83,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在誕生在胸中的  這不可動搖的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:26.54,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気と呼ぶため始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:26.54,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}稱為勇氣  讓我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:27.63,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Be Starters！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:27.63,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Be Starters！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:33.05,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}未知数のドアだって  怖がらず開けってね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:33.05,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}充滿未知數的門扉  也要毫無畏懼地去開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:35.43,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Flying far away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:35.43,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Flying far away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.68,0:02:41.31,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}舞い上がれ  彼方へと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.68,0:02:41.31,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}隨風飄揚  直到遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:49.72,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(858,0)\blur4}「妞!」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始就是新學期了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圍巾式固定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德克薩斯交叉固定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:02:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆蝦固定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還要晨練  就先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  就算習慣了  但一早就這麼搞還真是悲慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.87,0:03:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還認為我會洩露你的秘密嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為摯友  我相信著次郎你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.67,0:03:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是摯友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒能幫你克服女性恐懼症
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能這麼簡單就治好的話  就不用這麼辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.85,0:03:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二學期開始不得不用更猛烈的治療方案了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐也這麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  還請手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:03:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:03:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面的  快讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次郎  危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近衛？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.38,0:04:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起為次郎做人工呼吸時的情景了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來我和她接過吻…了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個男人準…準備接吻…居然還是在路邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你在興奮個什麼勁兒啊  沒種笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了躲避撞擊而變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了讓開了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你那車是怎麼搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在二手店殺價買的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你沒受傷吧  昴大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼連問候都差別那麼大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒受傷  宇佐美你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作…作為賠罪請您收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個要怎麼處理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是剛才宇佐美叼著的  算是間接KISS吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧  要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇跡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然會好好做作業
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是理所當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是作為在女僕咖啡廳打工的獎勵給你抄的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊…我說為什麼你會知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是順風耳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}（順風耳日語寫成地獄耳…）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…這話從你嘴裡說出來還真是恐怖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐  馬上就要上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  次郎同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是和昴一起吃午飯的吧  今天也加我一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  請用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是豪華的便當啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣儘管吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來分一下吧  當然也有昴的份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐  這種事就讓我來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  嘗嘗看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煮得嫩嫩的肉與濃郁的奶油醬汁完美結合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,產生一股絕妙的滋味  這是什麼料理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是一般的奶油濃湯而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.23,0:07:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近…近衛？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼月  近衛為什麼會變成這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是調味中加了白葡萄酒的緣故嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅加了一滴而已就變成這樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太敏感了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏感有什麼錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  沾上醬汁了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴  幫他擦一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.31,0:07:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解了  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這醬汁真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快快…快住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就是很好吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼月  快給我想想辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我阻止了她不就算不上治療了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我是你的摯友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也把你當做最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以快住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是為了維持這樣的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.91,0:08:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多嘴  這都是說了那些話的次郎的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那些話」是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次郎  我有話想對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  是你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.37,0:08:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是想怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼月？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是暫時讓她休息一下比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我把她搬到保健室嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是女人  我要專心…給我專心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才這傢伙是想說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,養眼  真是養眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.69,0:09:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新學期一來就讓我大飽了眼福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背負著受傷少年前進的眼鏡男
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中不斷吶喊著「活下去」…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次郎同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴的話已經讓她在保健室睡下了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…妞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.52,0:09:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  剛才那可愛的聲音是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:09:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  涼月？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道身體不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼這麼問啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  因為你發出了「妞」的聲音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幻聽了吧  好好想想  次郎同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能會發出這樣的聲音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.47,0:10:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是煩人啊  我說了什麼都沒有了妞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妞？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的妞  這是有原因的妞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用這種憐憫的眼神看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你發出的聲音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞎說  這才不是剛才那可愛的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的聲音啊妞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別扯蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妞～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  喉嚨感覺有點不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧  次郎同學  還是去下保健室比較好妞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:10:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:10:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妞～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…我有一個對學校裡任何人都沒有說過的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的妞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次郎同學  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唯一的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\fsp20}　妞{\r}\N煉乳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}妞{\fsp20}　{\r}\N乳牛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對保健室的老師做了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.03,0:11:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對著她的臉頰扇了兩三下後  她就哭著跑出去了妞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.59,0:11:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是錢扇臉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.26,0:11:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妞！妞！妞！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…所以說剛才的那個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是打嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打嗝？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的妞  我一開始打嗝就停不下來了妞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我聽起來你只是說話的時候在句尾加上了「妞」而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的打嗝有點與眾不同妞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現在句尾的情況比較多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這為什麼會成為你的弱點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我在周圍的人眼中看來似乎非常可愛妞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你是個心直口快的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但沒想到會如此這般自吹自擂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了妞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.97,0:12:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過實際上也確實挺可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次郎同學  你能幫我止住這個打嗝嗎妞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛居然打算擁抱涼月！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.49,0:12:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐的打嗝是充滿著魔性的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:12:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近衛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許你無法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到大小姐打嗝的人  尤其是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會被她的魅力所迷住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在騙人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去曾經因此引發過小小的騷亂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騷亂？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是大約10年前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時還在上小學的大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被邀請參加了某個宴會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妞！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妞！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來幫這位小姐止住打嗝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後連大小姐的保鏢和會場的保安也無法平息騷亂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得已之下只好出動了防暴隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼月家內部將此次騷亂稱為「打嗝之亂」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是規模何等龐大的蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4年前也發生了類似的騷亂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那時昴幫我平息了騷亂妞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:13:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～昴可真是名不虛傳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  昴是我最棒的管家妞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.64,0:14:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝大小姐的誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟在幹什麼啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}蹭蹭  好可愛啊～嗚呼呼～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.71,0:14:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  不…不是的  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不是因為平時冷酷的大小姐居然會發出這種聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人覺得真的好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  你差不多該放手了吧妞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  再這樣抱一會也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  對不起  我現在就放開您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.02,0:14:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近衛  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次郎給我閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.24,0:14:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說難道你也想從我這裡搶走可愛的大小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你突然間說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決不允許這種事情發生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你給肅清了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣  你冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴  你現在馬上回家把能止住打嗝的道具拿過來妞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來還有這種東西嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在這種情況下離開大小姐的身邊有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:15:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一見面立刻就想抱住我的管家一點用處都派不上妞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…您說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我就此告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在擔心昴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她回去真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就想讓她回去了妞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好動動腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道具之類的打個電話讓人送過來不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.09,0:15:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你為什麼要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想和你兩人獨處啊妞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次郎同學  希望你能告訴我妞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和昴之間究竟發生了什麼妞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴在面對你時態度的轉變
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.22,0:15:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也應該注意到了妞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對昴說了什麼妞？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我什麼也沒說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我從家裡拿來的用來止住打嗝的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的速度也太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來次郎  你的衣服怎麼亂成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且連大小姐也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…沒什麼大不了的  昴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是被次郎同學襲擊了一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是你襲擊我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  打嗝也止住了  讓我們回教室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  說起來你是什麼時候止住的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  次郎同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.95,0:16:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就止住了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說這是你唯一的弱點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你是故意的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子可是有著很多秘密的妞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:16:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是次郎同學真的是很體貼別人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:16:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和你兩人獨處  讓我感到有點開心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你在說些什麼莫名其妙的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊  我只是說著玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼月
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近衛  涼月
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐  能站得起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐？大小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼月同學出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼月家連醫院都有開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是扭傷了腳而已  你太大驚小怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.81,0:17:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  以防萬一還請您進行一下全面的檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明我陪在您的身邊卻還…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意  這不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我自己太不小心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會和爸爸好好說的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  你不必太過在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去為您準備些飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近衛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你好像傷得更重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:18:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這小子在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你也挺想住院的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.66,0:19:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有我陪伴左右  卻還讓大小姐受了傷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我回家休息去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我今天就留在醫院…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了讓你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.54,0:19:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我還要照顧大小姐的日常起居…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會替你照顧的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經不再是管家了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔  這究竟是為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她讓重要的大小姐受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為管家自然要負起責任
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.29,0:19:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴  至今為止你做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的非常努力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以好好休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決不允許昴辭去管家的職務
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  昴是我最棒的管家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐  這件事已經定下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會和父親商量的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會說服他的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當您的管家對於昴來說太過勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且辭去管家的職務的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就沒有必要繼續女扮男裝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.77,0:20:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為女孩子上學也是為了昴著想…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐  您要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用說嗎  自然是爸爸那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.19,0:20:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐  已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.49,0:20:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止承蒙您的關照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也有很多不足之處
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但能當上大小姐的管家我真的…真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到非常幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次郎同學  拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近衛  等等啊  近衛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不放
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算昏倒我也絕不會放手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.08,0:21:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要把煩惱全都埋藏在心底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.45,0:21:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲傷也好  後悔也罷  全都對著我發洩出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什麼我都會全部接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.83,0:21:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天早晨都被紅羽施加摔跤技  我可沒有白練
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.65,0:21:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.03,0:21:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.86,0:21:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也沒有必要繼續保守秘密了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.07,0:21:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我也要和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.63,0:21:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到極限了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近…衛…
